name: FoxFrenzyVR
summary: Welcome to FoxFrenzyVR! A Social Game with many things to do and with many new things to come in the bright future of this game. You could jump branch to branch to trampoline in the forest map. Go though all the tunnels and get a free cosmetic in zero gravity. Buy some spectacular fashion in the shop. Or just chill in the cove with nothing to fear but sharks upon the horizon. There is so much to do and there is so much to create that you can't ever be bored, unless you're by your self, In which case we...
